- provide(:title, "TextMy.Team | Text Your Contacts")
%section#LandingContainer
  .container
    .row
      .col-sm-12.col-md-8.col-lg-4
        .jumbotron
          %h1.text-white{style: 'font-weight: 900;'}
            %b
              Texting Is
            %br
            %b{style: 'font-size: 2em;'}
              %em NOW
          %br
          %p.text-white What do people always have in their hand? Their phone. Let's be honest: if you want your message read in a timely manner, you send a text. We make that easy.
          %br
          %a.btn.btn-success.btn-lg.btn-block{href: new_user_registration_path} See How

%section#Features
  .section-header
    .section-title
      .row
        .col-sm-12.col-md-8.col-lg-6.col-centered
          .text-center
            %hr
            %h1 How It Works
  .section-content
    .container
      .row
        .col-sm-6
          %h1
            BYO
            %img.img-fluid{src: asset_url('twilio-logo-red.svg')}
          %p
            Twilio is a cloud communications platform as a service company that allows software developers to programmatically make and receive phone calls and send and receive text messages using its web service APIs.
            TextMy.team uses the Twilio Connectâ„¢ platform to help you leverage Twilio's amazing capabilities, as well as its cost effective pay-as-you-go pricing,
            %em without having to write any code yourself.
          %p
            What makes TextMy.team different from most text messaging service providers is that because you connect
            %strong your own Twilio account,
            you pay
            %em cost
            for whatever your usage is. Instead of paying us a ridiculous per-message upcharge, you simply pay us a low monthly fee to make it easy to send & receive messages and manage your contact database.

          %p
            All TmT users must have a Twilio account connected for anything to work.
            %em Create yours today!

          .text-center
            %a.btn.btn-lg{href: "https://www.twilio.com/pricing", target: '_blank', style: "background-color: #0D122B; text-decoration: none; color: #fff"}
              %img.img-fluid{src: asset_url('twilio-mark-white.svg')}
              SIGN UP
        .col-sm-6
          %img.img-fluid.rounded{src: asset_url('https://www.twilio.com/marketing/bundles/company-brand/img/photo-twilio-whiteboard-hi-res.jpg')}



%section#Pricing
  .section-header
    .section-title
      .row
        .col-sm-12.col-md-8.col-lg-6.col-centered
          .text-center
            %hr
            %h1 Pricing
            %p.lead Choose the plan that makes the most sense for you.
            %span.text-muted
              Upgrade or downgrade at any time. TextMy.team monthly pricing
              %strong does not include
              Twilio usage costs.
  .section-content
    .container
      .row.flex-items-xs-middle.flex-items-xs-center
        / Table #1
        .col-xs-12.col-lg-4
          .card.text-xs-center
            .card-header
              %h4.card-title
                Solo Plan
              %h3.display-2
                %span.currency> $
                5
                %span.period / month
            .card-block
              %ul.list-group
                %li.list-group-item Twilio Integration
                %li.list-group-item One User
                %li.list-group-item One Managed Line
                %li.list-group-item Unlimited Contacts
                %li.list-group-item Unlimited Messages
                %li.list-group-item.text-danger
                  %em 0 support hours
              %a.btn.btn-primary.mt-3.btn-block.disabled{:href => "#"} Coming Soon!
        / Table #1
        .col-xs-12.col-lg-4
          .card.text-xs-center{style: "border-radius: 3px; border: 2px solid #5cb85c"}
            .card-header
              %h4.card-title
                Group Plan
              %h3.display-2
                %span.currency> $
                10
                %span.period / month
            .card-block
              %ul.list-group
                %li.list-group-item Twilio Integration
                %li.list-group-item Unlimited Users
                %li.list-group-item Unlimited Managed Lines
                %li.list-group-item Unlimited Contacts
                %li.list-group-item.text-success Contact Uploader
                %li.list-group-item Unlimited Messages
                %li.list-group-item.text-success
                  %em 2 support hours
              %a.btn.btn-primary.mt-3.btn-block.disabled{:href => "#"} Coming Soon!
        / Table #1
        .col-xs-12.col-lg-4
          .card.text-xs-center
            .card-header
              %h4.card-title
                Enterprise Plan
              %h3.display-2
                %span.currency> $
                50
                %span.period / month
            .card-block
              %ul.list-group
                %li.list-group-item Twilio Integration
                %li.list-group-item Unlimited Users
                %li.list-group-item Unlimited Managed Lines
                %li.list-group-item Unlimited Contacts
                %li.list-group-item.text-success Contact Uploader
                %li.list-group-item Unlimited Messages
                %li.list-group-item.text-success
                  %em 25 priority support hours
                %li.list-group-item.text-success
                  %em Feature Requests
                %li.list-group-item.text-success
                  %em Custom Integrations
              %a.btn.btn-primary.mt-3.btn-block{:href => "#"} Choose Plan
